CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781183478
OL,3,CMum calls for tighter carbon monoxide
OL,4,Claws after death of teenage couple
OL,6,FFive people have been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of gross negligence
OL,8,Fmanslaughter and released on
OL,9,Fconditional bail.
OL,11,FCherish's mum Devon Andrews said:
OL,12,F"Every day we wake up and you feel
OL,13,Flike it's going to be over. And it's
OL,14,Fnot. It's not ever going to be over.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781183478
OL,3,CMum calls for tighter carbon monoxide
OL,4,Claws after death of teenage couple
OL,6,F"I feel like I'm watching somebody
OL,7,Felse's horror movie - that's how I
OL,8,Ffeel. I feel like I look at myself sat
OL,9,Fat the grave and I think 'look at that
OL,10,Fpoor woman there crying for her
OL,11,Fdaughter'. But that poor woman's me.
OL,12,FAnd life will never be the same again."
OL,14,FDevon has set up a charity called The
OL,15,FCherish and Ethan Forever Foundation
OL,16,Fto campaign for changes to the law
OL,17,Faround carbon monoxide alarms in
OL,18,Fholiday accommodation.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
