PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781183478
OL,3,CMum calls for tighter carbon monoxide
OL,4,Claws after death of teenage couple
OL,6,FA petition online has attracted more
OL,7,Fthan 8,000 signatures and will be
OL,8,Fdebated in Parliament if it reaches
OL,9,F100,000.
OL,11,FIt is already a legal requirement for
OL,12,Fcarbon monoxide alarms to be installed
OL,13,Fin living accommodation where there is
OL,14,Fa gas or solid fuel-burning appliance
OL,15,Fbut Devon wants stronger enforcement
OL,16,Fof those rules.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
