PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781183478
OL,3,CMum calls for tighter carbon monoxide
OL,4,Claws after death of teenage couple
OL,6,FShe said: "How can that just be the
OL,7,Fend? That can't just be the end of
OL,8,FCherish and Ethan. That's why I won't
OL,9,Fstop - I won't stop until I succeed
OL,10,Fand even if I do succeed I still won't
OL,11,Fstop.
OL,13,F"If we could save one life after the
OL,14,Ffact, imagine being able to say that -
OL,15,Fwe did that in Cherish's name. It'd be
OL,16,Fworth it."
OL,18,FStephanie Trotter from The Carbon
OL,19,FMonoxide and Gas Safety Society is
OL,20,Fbacking Devon's calls.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781183478
OL,3,CMum calls for tighter carbon monoxide
OL,4,Claws after death of teenage couple
OL,6,FShe said: "The most important thing is
OL,7,Fto learn from theser tragedies and
OL,8,Fprevent future deaths and injuries. I
OL,9,Fthink all homes, all enclosed spaces,
OL,10,Fshould have to have a carbon monoxide
OL,11,Falarm as an absolute basic
OL,12,Frequirement."
OL,14,FThe Cherish and Ethan Forever
OL,15,FFoundation is aiming to change to law
OL,16,Fand also spread the word about the
OL,17,Fcarbon monoxide.
OL,19,FDevon herself is hoping to go into
OL,20,Fschools to tell Cherish and Ethan's
OL,21,Fstory.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781183478
OL,3,CMum calls for tighter carbon monoxide
OL,4,Claws after death of teenage couple
OL,6,FShe said: "It makes me feel like I'm
OL,7,Fstill being a mum. That's the only
OL,8,Freason why. It's not about money, it's
OL,9,Fnot about politics.
OL,11,F"It's about me feeling like I'm still
OL,12,Fbeing Cherish's mum, still living for
OL,13,Fher. Still doing things for her every
OL,14,Fday."
OL,16,FITV News has made several attempts to
OL,17,Fcontact the company which runs Little
OL,18,FEden Country Park, where the teenagers
OL,19,Fwere staying when they died, but has
OL,20,Fnot a response.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/7
